Reply to a calendar invite

Usage: mxr invite reply [OPTIONS] <MESSAGE_ID> <ACTION>

Arguments:
  <MESSAGE_ID>
  <ACTION>      [possible values: accept, tentative, decline]

Options:
      --dry-run
      --format <FORMAT>  [possible values: table, json, jsonl, csv, ids]
  -h, --help             Print help
